"guisubmenu></menuchoice>. De valgte kan trækkes rundt i &dolphin;-vinduet "
"ved at klikke og trække i panelets titel. De tilgængelige paneler beskrives "
"herunder."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid "Places"
msgstr "Steder"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:695
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is found at the left of the window "
#| "by default, The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel shows any locations you "
#| "have bookmarked. It also shows any disk or media attached to the "
#| "computer. This list corresponds with the list of places in the "
#| "breadcrumbs menu."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel is located at the left of the window "
"by default. The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> panel shows any locations you "
"have bookmarked. It also shows any disk or media attached to the computer, "
"recently accessed items and allows you to search for certain type of files. "
"The order of these entries can be changed by drag and drop."
msgstr ""
"Panelet <guilabel>Steder</guilabel> findes som standard i vinduets venstre "
"side. <guilabel>Steder</guilabel> viser de steder du har bogmærket. Det "
