#~ msgid "&dolphin; Features"
#~ msgstr "Funktioner i &dolphin;"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&dolphin; does not represent a wild departure from the &konqueror; file "
#~ "manager interface. There are certain paradigms in use however, which may "
#~ "require some readjustment on the user's part. An attempt is made below to "
#~ "explain these in an effort to provide a more enjoyable experience for our "
#~ "users."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&dolphin; repræsenterer ikke den store afvigelse fra brugerfladen i "
#~ "&konqueror;'s filhåndtering. Der er dog nogle paradigmer i brug, som kan "
#~ "kræve at brugeren omstiller sig. Et forsøg er gjort herunder for at "
#~ "forklare disse med det formål at tilbyde vores brugere en mere behagelig "
#~ "oplevelse."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The default &dolphin; interface consists of a (1) menu bar, (2) toolbar, "
#~ "(3) location bar, (4) workspace, (6) Places Panel, (7) Information Panel "
#~ "and (8) status bar."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Brugerfladen i &dolphin; består af (1) menulinje, (2) værktøjslinje, (3) "
#~ "stedlinje, (4) arbejdsområde, (6) sted-panel, (7) informationspanel og "
#~ "(8) statuslinje."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The location bar displays the path to the current folder. The location "
#~ "bar has two versions. By default location is chosen through the 'bread "
#~ "crumb' display. The bread crumb display makes each folder a link which "
#~ "can be used to immediately go to the entry. The <filename class="
#~ "\"directory\">/home/peter/Documents</filename> entry in the bread crumb "
#~ "view would become 'Home > peter > Documents' with Home, peter, and "
#~ "Documents being clickable links which are able go to there respective "
#~ "locations. This makes navigation to folders above the current folder "
#~ "easier and more intuitive. There is also the classic \"location view\" "
#~ "which is a text box in which you can type the full path of the folder you "
#~ "wish to view."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Stedlinjen viser stien til den aktuelle mappe. Stedlinjen findes i to "
#~ "versioner. Som standard vælges stedet gennem \"bread crumb\"-displayet. "
#~ "Dette \"bread crumb\"-display gør hver mappe til et link, der kan bruges "
#~ "til at gå direkte til mappen. Indgangen <filename class=\"directory\">/"
#~ "home/peter/Documents </filename> vil i \"bread crumb\"-visning blive til "
#~ "\"Hjemmemappe > peter > Documents\", hvor Hjemmemappe, peter, og "
#~ "Documents bliver links der kan klikkes på for at gå til deres respektive "
#~ "steder. Dette gør navigation til mapper over den aktuelle mappe nemmere "
#~ "og mere intuitivt. Der er også den klassiske \"sted-visning\" der er et "
#~ "tekstfelt hvor du kan angive den fulde søgesti til den mappe du vil have "
#~ "vist."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To switch from breadcrumbs to location view, simply click to the right of "
#~ "the breadcrumb area. To change back, click the newly appeared yellow "
#~ "arrow to the right of the location bar."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "For at skifte fra \"breadcrumbs\"- til sted-visning klikkes ganske enkelt "
#~ "til højre for \"breadcrumb\"-området. Klik på den gule pil, der kommer "
#~ "frem til højre for stedlinjen, for at skifte tilbage."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To change the default &dolphin; view, please see the settings section."
#~ msgstr "Se opsætnings-sektionen for at ændre standardvisningen i &dolphin;."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The workspace shows the contents of the current folder. The workspace can "
#~ "also be set to \"Split\" mode and show two folders simultaneously."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Arbejdsområdet viser indholdet af den aktuelle mappe. Arbejdsområdet kan "
#~ "også sættes i tilstanden \"Opdelt\" og vise to mapper samtidigt."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The status bar shows a limited amount of data relating to the file "
#~ "hovered over and the current folder. When a file is hovered over, the "
#~ "status bar shows the file name, the filesize and the file type &eg; JPEG. "
#~ "When no file has been highlighted or hovered over, the status bar shows "
#~ "the amount of files and folders in the current folder. At all times the "
#~ "status bar shows the amount of storage space that has currently been used "
#~ "on the current mount point, as well as the maximum space available on the "
#~ "mount point &eg; <filename class=\"directory\">/home/</filename>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Statuslinjen viser en begrænset mængde data i relation til den fil, musen "
#~ "føres over, og den aktuelle mappe. Når musen føres over en fil viser "
#~ "statuslinjen filens navn, størrelse og type som f.eks. JPEG. Hvis ingen "
#~ "fil er markeret, eller ingen mus føres hen over, viser statuslinjen "
#~ "antallet af filer og mapper i den aktuelle mappe. Statuslinjen viser "
#~ "altid den opbrugte mængde af lagerplads på det aktuelle monteringspunkt "
#~ "samt det maksimalt tilgængelige plads på monteringspunktet som f.eks. "
#~ "<filename class=\"directory\">/home/</filename>."

#~ msgid "&dolphin; Workspace"
#~ msgstr "Arbejdsområdet i &dolphin;"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The &dolphin; workspace can display the contents of a folder in a variety "
#~ "of views. There are three viewing modes Icons, Details, and Columns. Each "
#~ "of these can have Preview enabled. This changes the icons into showing a "
#~ "preview of the file, rather than an simply icon."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Arbejdsområdet i &dolphin; kan vise mappers indhold på flere måder. Der "
#~ "findes tre visnings-tilstande: Ikoner, Detaljer og Kolonner. Hver af "
#~ "disse kan have forhåndsvisning aktiveret. Dette ændrer ikoner til at "
#~ "forhåndsvise filen, i stedet for at vise et simpelt ikon."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <guibutton>Icons</guibutton> view shows the contents of the folder "
#~ "via the file icon type &eg; an <acronym>MP3</acronym> file will be "
#~ "represented with the icon for an <acronym>MP3</acronym> file. Sub-folders "
#~ "are represented in the form of a folder icon. The folder icon is defined "
#~ "by the &kde; icon theme currently in use, however individual folders can "
#~ "have their icon changed manually if the user wishes. This can be done via "
#~ "the properties dialog."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "I visningen <guibutton>Ikoner</guibutton> ses mappens indhold via filens "
#~ "ikon-type. En <acronym>MP3</acronym>-fil vises f.eks. med ikonet for en "
#~ "<acronym>MP3</acronym>-fil. Undermapper vises i form af et mappeikon. "
#~ "Mappeikonet defineres af det ikontema der aktuelt anvendes i &kde;, dog "
#~ "kan individuelle mappers ikoner ændres manuelt, hvis brugeren ønsker "
#~ "dette. Dette kan gøres via dialogen \"Egenskaber\"."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <guibutton>Details</guibutton> view lists the contents of a folder "
#~ "whilst also displaying additional properties about the file. The default "
#~ "&dolphin; configuration only displays the size of the file and the date "
#~ "it was last modified. The choice of additional information shown can be "
#~ "changed by right clicking on the column header and selecting the "
#~ "information you wish to view or in <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#~ "guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure &dolphin;...</guisubmenu></menuchoice>"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "I visningen <guibutton>Detaljer</guibutton> ses en liste over en mappes "
#~ "indhold, mens filens yderligere egenskaber også vises. "
#~ "Standardkonfigurationen for &dolphin; viser kun filens størrelse og "
#~ "datoen for sidste ændring. Valg om visning af yderligere information kan "
#~ "ændres ved at højreklikke kolonnens header og vælge den information du "
#~ "gerne vil se, eller via  <menuchoice><guimenu> Opsætning</"
#~ "guimenu><guisubmenu>Indstil &dolphin;...</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <guibutton>Preview</guibutton> view is similar to the icons view. The "
#~ "difference is that wherever possible previews of the files are shown. "
#~ "This function works for a number of image types including; JPG, PNG, XCF, "
#~ "<acronym>SVG</acronym> and numerous others. The previews view is also "
#~ "capable of showing the first 14 lines from text documents. &dolphin; is "
#~ "also capable of displaying a preview of &HTML; and <acronym>PDF</acronym> "
#~ "files in the previews view. It is also possible to modify the size of the "
#~ "previews via the Configure &dolphin; dialog."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Det der ses i <guibutton>Forhåndsvisning</guibutton> minder meget om "
#~ "ikonvisning. Forskellen er at filerne forhåndsvises altid, hvis det er "
#~ "muligt. Denne funktion virker med et antal billedfil-typer inklusive JPG, "
#~ "PNG, XCF, <acronym>SVG </acronym> og et utal af andre. Forhåndsvisningen "
#~ "er også i stand til at vise de første 14 linjer af et tekstdokument. "
#~ "&dolphin; kan også forhåndsvise &HTML;- og <acronym>PDF</acronym>-filer i "
#~ "denne visning. Det er tillige muligt at ændre størrelsen af "
#~ "forhåndsvisninger via dialogen \"Indstil &dolphin;...\"."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Changing the view of the folder a user is working in is as simple as "
#~ "clicking the icon of the view they wish to use. This will cause the "
#~ "workspace view to change accordingly."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Visningen af den mappe, en bruger arbejder i, ændres ved ganske enkelt at "
#~ "klikke på ikonet for den visning brugeren vil benytte. I overensstemmelse "
#~ "med dette ændres visningen af arbejdsområdet."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The workspace in &dolphin; is capable of showing two folders within the "
#~ "same window, known as split workspaces. In order to enable or disable the "
#~ "split workspace mode toggle the icon on the taskbar. Another way to "
#~ "enable or disable the split workspace mode is to use the "
#~ "<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Split</guimenuitem></"
#~ "menuchoice> menu option."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Arbejdsområdet i &dolphin; er i stand til at vise to mapper i det samme "
#~ "vindue, kendt som opdelt arbejdsområde. Slå ikonet \"Opdel\" til eller "
#~ "fra for at hhv. aktivere eller deaktivere det opdelte arbejdsområde. En "
#~ "anden måde at aktivere eller deaktivere opdelt arbejdsområde er via "
#~ "menuen <menuchoice><guimenu>Vis </guimenu><guimenuitem>Opdel</"
#~ "guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If this option is enabled then the workspace will split apart. Two "
#~ "separate workspace areas will be available for use, along with two "
#~ "separate location bars. Clicking on either workspace will make it the "
#~ "active workspace. If the user toggles the split workspace mode off, then "
#~ "the currently active workspace will remain, while the inactive workspace "
#~ "will close."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Hvis denne indstilling aktiveres deles arbejdsområdet op. To separate "
#~ "arbejdsområder stilles til rådighed sammen med to separate stedlinjer. "
#~ "Ved at klikke i et af områderne gøres dette til det aktive arbejdsområde. "
#~ "Hvis brugeren slår opdelt visning fra, forbliver det aktive "
#~ "arbejdsområde, mens det inaktive lukkes."

#~ msgid "&dolphin; In Split Workspace Mode"
#~ msgstr "&dolphin; i tilstanden opdelt arbejdsområde"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&dolphin; is capable of remembering the workspace view on a per-folder "
#~ "basis. For example, if while viewing <filename class=\"directory\">/home/"
#~ "peter/Pictures/</filename> the user choses to use the preview view, then "
#~ "the next time the user enters that folder, the view will be changed to "
#~ "the preview view. This is especially useful for folders containing mainly "
#~ "images. The feature only works for local folders which the user has read/"
#~ "write permissions to. &dolphin; will also remember the viewing mode it "
#~ "was in when last running &eg; single workspace or split workspace."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&dolphin; er i stand til at huske arbejdsområdets visning baseret på hver "
#~ "enkelt mappe. Hvis f.eks. brugeren vælger at aktivere \"Forhåndsvisning\" "
#~ "for mappen <filename class=\"directory\">/home/peter/Pictures/</filename> "
#~ "ændres visningen til dette næste gang brugeren går ind i den mappe. Dette "
#~ "er specielt nyttigt for mapper der hovedsageligt indeholder billeder. "
#~ "Funktionen virker kun for lokale mapper hvortil brugeren har både læse- "
#~ "og skriverettigheder. &dolphin; vil også huske den visning, der var aktiv "
#~ "da den kørte sidste gang som f.eks. enkelt eller opdelt arbejdsområde."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&dolphin; can also display files and sub-folders that are hidden in the "
#~ "current folder &eg; files such as <filename>.dolphin</filename> and sub-"
#~ "folder such as <filename class=\"directory\">.kde/</filename>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&dolphin; kan også vise skjulte filer og undermapper i den aktuelle mappe "
#~ "f.eks. filer som <filename>.dolphin</filename> og undermapper som "
#~ "<filename class=\"directory\">.kde/</filename>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Hidden files and sub-folders can be distinguished from non-hidden file "
#~ "and sub-folders by their colouring. Hidden files/sub-folders are fainter "
#~ "than non-hidden files/sub-folders."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Skjulte filer og undermapper kan kendes fra de ikke-skjulte filer og "
#~ "undermapper via deres farvetone. De skjulte filer og undermapper er "
#~ "svagere i farven end de ikke-skjulte."

#~ msgid "&dolphin; Showing Hidden Files/Sub-folders Enabled"
#~ msgstr "&dolphin; med visning af skjulte filer/undermapper aktiveret"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&dolphin; is able to sort the contents of a folder in a number of ways. "
#~ "These are; By Name, By Date, By Size and Descending order. These only "
#~ "apply to the current folder the user is currently in and do not affect "
#~ "other folders. As with the Views Modes the Sorting order is saved for "
#~ "this folder."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&dolphin; kan sortere mappers indhold på flere måder. Disse er: efter "
#~ "navn, efter dato, efter størrelse og i nedadgående orden. Dette gælder "
#~ "kun for den aktuelle mappe og har ikke indflydelse på andre mapper. Lige "
#~ "som med visningstilstande gemmes sorteringsrækkefølgen for denne mappe."

#~ msgid "&dolphin; Panels"
#~ msgstr "Paneler i &dolphin;"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The main feature of &dolphin; that allows navigation of the file system "
#~ "is the work space. Clicking on a sub-folder within the current folder "
#~ "changes to this folder. Clicking on files within the workspace will open "
#~ "the file in the default application for that file type."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Hovedfunktionen i &dolphin;, der muliggør navigation i filsystemet, er "
#~ "arbejdsområdet. At klikke på en undermappe i den aktuelle mappe skifter "
#~ "til denne mappe. At klikke på filer i arbejdsområdet vil åbne filen i det "
#~ "program der er standard for denne filtype."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The toolbar is also used for navigating the file system. The toolbar "
#~ "contains two buttons essential for navigating the file system quickly and "
#~ "easily, these are; <guiicon>Back</guiicon> and <guiicon>Forward</guiicon>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Værktøjslinjen bruges også til navigation i filsystemet. Værktøjslinjen "
#~ "har to essentielle knapper til navigation i filsystemet, disse er "
#~ "<guiicon>Tilbage </guiicon> og <guiicon>Fremad</guiicon>."

#~ msgid "&dolphin; Toolbar Buttons"
#~ msgstr "Værktøjslinje-knapper i &dolphin;"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Other buttons can be added to the toolbar to further aid navigation or to "
#~ "provide shortcuts for functions within &dolphin; &eg; deleting a file."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Andre knapper kan tilføjes værktøjslinjen for yderligere at hjælpe "
#~ "navigationen eller som genveje til funktioner i &dolphin; som f.eks. at "
#~ "slette en fil."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&dolphin; continually shows the folder that it is currently viewing the "
#~ "contents of, via the location bar and the title bar. The location bar has "
#~ "two views available. The first is the folder path view. This shows the "
#~ "path to the current folder &eg; <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/share/"
#~ "apps/dolphin/</filename>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&dolphin; viser fortsat den mappe, hvis indhold aktuelt ses, via "
#~ "stedlinjen og titellinjen. Stedlinjen har to tilgængelige visninger. Den "
#~ "første er mappens søgesti. Denne viser stien til den aktuelle mappe som f."
#~ "eks. <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/share/apps/dolphin/</filename>."

#~ msgid "&dolphin; Displaying The Folder Path View"
#~ msgstr "&dolphin; med visning af mappens søgesti"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The second view is the breadcrumb view. This allows the user to move to a "
#~ "folder a number of folders back from the current one. This is achieved "
#~ "via a tab like interface where the name of each previous folder is "
#~ "displayed and can be clicked on to change into."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Den anden visning er breadcrumb-visningen. Denne lader brugeren flytte et "
#~ "antal mapper tilbage fra den aktuelle. Dette opnås via en "
#~ "fanebladslignende brugerflade, hvor hver mappe vises og kan klikkes på "
#~ "for at skifte dertil."

#~ msgid "&dolphin; Displaying The Breadcrumb View"
#~ msgstr "&dolphin; med breadcrumb-visning"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To switch from breadcrumbs to location view, simply click in the right "
#~ "part of the breadcrumb area or use <menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> "
#~ "<guisubmenu>Navigation Bar</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Edit Location</"
#~ "guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. To change back, click the newly appeared "
#~ "yellow arrow to the right of the location bar or use <menuchoice> "
#~ "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Navigation Bar</guisubmenu> "
#~ "<guimenuitem>Show Full Location</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "For at skifte fra breadcrumbs- til sted-visning gøres ganske enkelt ved "
#~ "at klikke i højre del af  breadcrumb-området eller med <menuchoice> "
#~ "<guimenu> Vis</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Navigationslinje</guisubmenu> "
#~ "<guimenuitem> Redigérbar adresse</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Klik på den "
#~ "nyligt fremkomne gule pil til højre for stedlinjen eller brug "
#~ "<menuchoice> <guimenu>Vis</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Navigationslinje</"
#~ "guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Vis hele stien</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#~ msgid "&dolphin; Browse Button"
#~ msgstr "Opslagsknap i &dolphin;"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "With the folder path view the user is able to enter the whole path to the "
#~ "folder they wish to enter. In order to do so, the user can toggle the "
#~ "browse button to the folder path view or alternatively via the menu "
#~ "<menuchoice> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Navigation Bar</"
#~ "guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Edit Location</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> then "
#~ "enter the path to the folder they wish to enter. The user will notice as "
#~ "they are entering the path, a box will open underneath the address bar "
#~ "showing the content of the folder they are currently heading to. The "
#~ "content of this box will change as they continue to enter the path to the "
#~ "folder, showing the folders and the files beginning with the characters "
#~ "being entered &eg; <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/share/apps/k</"
#~ "filename> would display everything within the folder beginning with the k "
#~ "character."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Med visning af mappers søgesti kan brugeren angive den fulde søgesti til "
#~ "den ønskede mappe. For at gøre dette kan brugeren skifte opslagsknappen "
#~ "om til visning af mappers søgesti, eller alternativt via menuen "
#~ "<menuchoice> <guimenu>Vis</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Navigationslinje</"
#~ "guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Redigérbar adresse</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
#~ "og derefter angive stien til den ønskede mappe. Brugeren vil bemærke at "
#~ "eftersom stien indtastes, åbner en boks nedenunder med indholdet af den "
#~ "mappe, der i øjeblikket stiles mod. Indholdet af denne boks ændres "
#~ "eftersom stien til mappen fortsat indtastes, og viser mapper og filer der "
#~ "begynder med de tegn der indtastes. Eksempelvis ville <filename class="
#~ "\"directory\">/usr/share/apps/k </filename> vise alt i denne mappe der "
#~ "begynder med bogstavet \"k\"."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If the breadcrumb view is enabled then the user is unable to enter the "
#~ "path to the folder. The user must manually navigate the file system by "
#~ "clicking the folders and sub-folders within the folders."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Hvis breadcrumb-visning aktiveres kan brugeren ikke angive stien til "
#~ "mappen. Brugeren skal manuelt navigere ved at klikke på mapperne og deres "
#~ "undermapper."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In order to aid the navigation of the file system, &dolphin; can use "
#~ "Places. Places can be set for any location on the file system including "
#~ "virtual folders such as \"trash:/\". Selecting a Place will display that "
#~ "folder or virtual folder in the workspace."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Til at hjælpe med navigation i filsystemet kan &dolphin; bruge \"Steder"
#~ "\". Steder kan sættes for enhver placering i filsystemet inklusive "
#~ "virtuelle mapper som \"trash:/\". At vælge et sted vil vise denne mappe - "
#~ "eller virtuelle mappe - i arbejdsområdet."

#~ msgid "&dolphin; Bookmark Button Open"
#~ msgstr "&dolphin; med bogmærkeknappen åben"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In order to select a Place, the location bar must be set to the "
#~ "breadcrumb view. Clicking the image of the home button (as set by the "
#~ "icon theme currently in use) will drop down a list of all the available "
#~ "bookmarks. The &dolphin; Places Panel also contains your Places list. "
#~ "This can be accessed via switching the sidebar to bookmarks mode. The "
#~ "user then clicks the desired Place to open that folder."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "For at vælge et sted skal stedlinjen sættes til breadcrumb-visning. Ved "
#~ "at klikke på billedet af knappen for hjemmemappen (som sat af det aktuelt "
#~ "valgte ikon-tema) vises en liste over alle tilgængelige bogmærker. "
#~ "Panelet \"Steder\" i &dolphin; indeholder også en liste over steder. "
#~ "Denne kan tilgås ved at skifte sidebjælken til bogmærke-tilstand. "
#~ "Brugeren kan så klikke på stedet for at åbne mappen."

#~ msgid "&dolphin; Configuration"
#~ msgstr "Konfiguration af &dolphin;"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In order to configure &dolphin; the user needs to access the &dolphin; "
#~ "Configuration dialog. This can be accessed via the menu bar; <menuchoice> "
#~ "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &dolphin;...</"
#~ "guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "For at indstille &dolphin; skal brugeren gå til &dolphin;'s "
#~ "konfigurationsdialog. Denne kan tilgås via menulinjen <menuchoice> "
#~ "<guimenu>Opsætning</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Indstil &dolphin;...</"
#~ "guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The &dolphin; Configuration dialog consists of three sections; "
#~ "<guilabel>Startup</guilabel>, <guilabel>View Modes</guilabel>, and "
#~ "<guilabel>General</guilabel>. Clicking one of these sections will make "
#~ "those options available accordingly. The options available are displayed "
#~ "to the right of the dialog."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Konfigurationsdialogen i &dolphin; består af tre sektioner: "
#~ "<guilabel>Opstart</guilabel>, <guilabel>Visningstilstande</guilabel> og "
#~ "<guilabel>Generelt</guilabel>. At klikke på en af sektionerne gør denne "
#~ "tilgængelig. De tilgængelige valgmuligheder vises til højre i dialogen."

#, fuzzy
#~| msgid "&dolphin; Configuration Window Showing The View Options"
#~ msgid "&dolphin; Configuration Window Showing The Startup Options"
#~ msgstr "Konfigurationsvinduet i &dolphin; med valgmulighederne for visning"

#, fuzzy
#~| msgid ""
#~| "The <guilabel>General</guilabel> option allows users to set a number of "
#~| "options for &dolphin;, these are; the default home location for the user "
#~| "&eg; /home/Peter, the default view mode (all folders will use this view "
#~| "unless they have already been changed) and wether or not split view is "
#~| "enabled by default."
#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <guilabel>Startup</guilabel> option allows users to set a number of "
#~ "options for &dolphin;, these are; the default home location for the user "
#~ "&eg; /home/Peter, the default view mode (all folders will use this view "
#~ "unless they have already been changed) and whether or not split view is "
#~ "enabled by default."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Under <guilabel>Generelt</guilabel> kan brugeren indstille et antal af "
#~ "&dolphin;'s valgmuligheder. Disse standarder kan indstilles: brugerens "
#~ "hjemmemappe &eg; /home/Peter, visningstilstand (alle mapper vil bruge "
#~ "denne visning medmindre de allerede er blevet ændret) og om opdelt "
#~ "visning aktiveres eller ej."

#~ msgid "&dolphin; Configuration Window Showing The View Options"
#~ msgstr "Konfigurationsvinduet i &dolphin; med valgmulighederne for visning"

#, fuzzy
#~| msgid ""
#~| "The <guilabel>View Modes</guilabel> option differs slightly from the "
#~| "<guilabel>General</guilabel> option in that it has four tabs in the "
#~| "options. The <guilabel>Icons</guilabel> tab allows users to set options "
#~| "to do with the Icons View Mode &eg; icon size. The <guilabel>Details</"
#~| "guilabel> tab allows users to set options relating to the Details View "
#~| "Mode &eg; what information about files are shown. The Previews to allows "
#~| "users to set options relating to the Previews View Mode &eg; the size of "
#~| "the preview images."
#~ msgid ""
#~ "The <guilabel>View Modes</guilabel> option differs slightly from the "
#~ "<guilabel>Startup</guilabel> option in that it has three tabs in the "
#~ "options. The <guilabel>Icons</guilabel> tab allows users to set options "
#~ "to do with the Icons View Mode &eg; icon size. The <guilabel>Details</"
#~ "guilabel> tab allows users to set options relating to the Details View "
#~ "Mode &eg; what information about files are shown. The Previews to allows "
#~ "users to set options relating to the Previews View Mode &eg; the size of "
#~ "the preview images."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Sektionen <guilabel>Visningstilstande</guilabel> har, i modsætning til "
#~ "<guilabel>Generelt</guilabel>, fire faneblade med indstillinger. Under "
#~ "fanebladet <guilabel> Ikoner</guilabel> kan brugeren indstille "
#~ "visningstilstanden for ikoner som f.eks. størrelse på ikoner. "
#~ "Indstillingerne under <guilabel>Detaljer</guilabel> er relateret til "
#~ "visning af detaljer som f.eks. hvilke informationer om filer der skal "
#~ "vises. Under forhåndsvisning kan brugeren indstille tilstanden for "
#~ "forhåndsvisning som f.eks. størrelsen på forhåndsvisningsbillederne."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To quickly create a bookmark of the folder currently being viewed, right "
#~ "click in the work space and via the menu select \"Add to Places\". The "
#~ "Bookmarking dialog will open, enter a name for the bookmark along with an "
#~ "icon to represent the bookmark."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "For hurtigt at oprette et bogmærke for en mappe, der aktuelt vises, "
#~ "højreklikkes i arbejdsområdet og via menuen vælges \"Tilføj til Steder\". "
#~ "Bogmærkningsdialogen vil åbne og her angives et navn for bogmærket sammen "
#~ "med et ikon til at representere bogmærket."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&dolphin; is capable of comparing a selection of files to see the "
#~ "differences between them. For a user to be able to compare files then the "
#~ "&kompare; application must be installed. &dolphin; can only compare the "
#~ "files that &kompare; is capable on analyzing."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&dolphin; er i stand til at sammenligne et udvalg af filer for at se "
#~ "forskellene mellem disse. For at en bruger kan sammenligne filer skal "
#~ "programmet &kompare; installeres. &dolphin; kan kun sammenligne de filer "
#~ "&kompare; er i stand til at analysere."

#~ msgid "Filter A Selection Of Files"
#~ msgstr "Filtrere et udvalg af filer"

