#~ msgid "Frequently asked Questions"
#~ msgstr "Ofte stillede spørgsmål"

#~ msgid "How do I add my own custom service menus to &dolphin;?"
#~ msgstr "Hvordan kan jeg føje mine egne tjenestemenuer til &dolphin;?"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "&dolphin; can use the majority of service menus created for &konqueror;, "
#~ "however &dolphin; does impose one limitation on the service menus: "
#~ "Service menu entries that add themselves to the top level of the context "
#~ "menu will automatically be placed below the Actions sub-menu. This "
#~ "prevents that the context menu will get crowded."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&dolphin; kan bruge størstedelen af de tjenester der er lavet til "
#~ "&konqueror;, men &dolphin; sætter dog en begrænsning på tjenestemenuerne: "
#~ "Punkter i tjenestemenuer, der føjer sig selv til i toppen af kontekst-"
#~ "menuen, bliver automatisk placeret nedenunder handlings-undermenuerne. "
#~ "Dette forhindrer at kontekst-menuen bliver overfyldt."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To add a custom service menu to &dolphin; save the service menu to the "
#~ "&dolphin; service menu folder, this can be found in /home/house/.kde/"
#~ "share/apps/dolphin/servicemenus/. If the servicemenus sub-folder does not "
#~ "exist in the &dolphin; folder, then create the sub-folder and save the "
#~ "service menu to that folder. The next time the user launch &dolphin; the "
#~ "service menu will be available."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "For at føje en tjenestemenu til &dolphin; gemmes denne i tjenestemenu-"
#~ "mappen for &dolphin;, som findes i /home/house/.kde/share/apps/dolphin/"
#~ "servicemenus/. Opret undermappen \"servicemenus\", hvis den ikke findes i "
#~ "&dolphin;-mappen, og gem tjenestemenuen deri. Næste gang brugeren starter "
#~ "&dolphin; vil tjenestemenuen være tilgængelig."

#~ msgid "How do I make &dolphin; my default file manager?"
#~ msgstr "Hvordan gør jeg &dolphin; til min standard-filhåndtering?"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To make &dolphin; the default file manager for &kde; from the &kde; "
#~ "control center open the File Associations section via; &kde; "
#~ "Components>File Associations. If the user adds &dolphin; to the list of "
#~ "applications for the folder mime type and make it the first choice, then "
#~ "&dolphin; will become the default application to open any folder with. "
#~ "The folder mime type can be found by expanding the inode section of Known "
#~ "Types."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "For at gøre &dolphin; til standard-filhåndteringen i &kde; åbnes &kde;'s "
#~ "\"Systemopsætning\" og under fanebladet \"Avanceret\"  klikkes på "
#~ "\"Filassociationer\". Hvis brugeren føjer &dolphin; til listen over "
#~ "programmer for mappers mimetype, og sætter den som første valg, bliver "
#~ "&dolphin; standard- programmet til at åbne enhver mappe. Mappens mimetype "
#~ "kan findes ved at folde inode-sektionen over kendte typer ud."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To make &dolphin; the default file manager for the virtual folders "
#~ "created by &kde; &eg; system:/ then again in the File Associations "
#~ "section of the control center expand the inode section of Known Types. "
#~ "Under the system_directory mime type, add &dolphin; to the list of "
#~ "applications, however instead of choosing &dolphin; from the kmenu, type "
#~ "the following in to the text box at the top; dolphin %u. The virtual "
#~ "folders created by &kde; will then be opened by &dolphin; as default."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "For at gøre &dolphin; til standard-filhåndtering for virtuelle mapper, "
#~ "oprettet af &kde;, som f.eks. system:/ foldes inode-sektionen over kendte "
#~ "typer igen ud under \"Filassociationer\" i \"Systemopsætning\". Føj "
#~ "&dolphin; til listen over programmer under mimetype i system_directory. "
#~ "dog kan man, i stedet for at vælge &dolphin; fra kmenu, indtaste følgende "
#~ "tekst i tekstfeltet for oven: dolphin %u. De virtuelle mapper, oprettet "
#~ "af &kde;, åbnes derefter som standard af &dolphin;."

